Subject: Secunia Research: Microsoft Windows usp10.dll "GetFontDesc()" Integer Underflow Vulnerability

====================================================================== 
 
                    Secunia Research 08/12/2015              

             Microsoft Windows usp10.dll "GetFontDesc()"
                  Integer Underflow Vulnerability

====================================================================== 
